Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.58,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.53,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:15.92,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:20.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'd say there's actually too \Nmuch nothing happening in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.12,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,They say "inscrutable are \Nthe ways of Heaven,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe things go better when \Nthere's a little something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.41,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:32.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That just means nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:38.73,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:39.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, Mameshiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:43.31,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,You always say all that hopeless stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:46.30,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,but when you're down, \Nyou sound even more hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:50.83,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.00,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with \NYui-san and Yukino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Did they say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.51,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:01.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:05.34,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:08.29,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you just assume that I did something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:13.03,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you might have done something \Nwithout realizing it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.23,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine. Tell me every detail, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:18.97,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:24.34,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:26.22,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,What, again with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:28.03,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:31.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting pushy. Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.99,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.57,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What did I say that wasn't normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:39.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You were being pushy, \Nand it was annoying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:43.70,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:46.59,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I won't ask anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:48.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.47,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving now. Remember to lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:57.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.29,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Something totally happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.53,Ore_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.03,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.37,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:53.34,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A world that wants nothing to change... \Nthat wants stagnation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.35,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hachiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:02.51,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.66,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.07,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that was a \Npretty normal greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:08.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.25,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:02.92,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and that crêpe place \Nby the station is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.78,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.61,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go there together, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.59,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,The choco-banana is be—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.04,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.85,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Neveryone seemed pretty normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:43.63,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, uh... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.10,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing seemed out of place \Nas far as I could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.66,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:57.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was pretty nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.98,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,but now it's like I shouldn't \Nhave been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.98,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,They're all... totally normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.43,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're thinking anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:15.18,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,We could never tell what he was \Nthinking in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.86,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.19,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,understanding each other is another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:23.28,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no point in worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it best for us to just be normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.43,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,We should be normal, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.03,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.87,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:39.40,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's normal for you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.38,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,To not change, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:47.92,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.51,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.91,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.97,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.14,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.78,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you guys a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.87,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing. Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.11,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You can come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.87,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.81,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Shiromeguri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.25,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:23.93,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-senpai! Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.00,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello! It's been ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.51,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You're running for student \Ncouncil president?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.26,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.83,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought I don't seem \Ncut out for that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.31,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I get that all the time, so I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.69,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That I seem slow, or dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.14,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So, is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:54.93,Ore_Main,Megumi,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki-san is running for \Nstudent council president,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:57.45,Ore_Main,Megumi,0000,0000,0000,,but, well... how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.37,Ore_Main,Megumi,0000,0000,0000,,We want to make sure she's not elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:05.11,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Then you don't want to be \Nthe student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.80,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.82,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't volunteer myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.72,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else put me in the running.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.43,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what is this? What idol are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.97,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say I \Nstand out, in a bad way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.18,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She does seem like the type that \Nother girls would despise, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:24.45,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the soccer team manager, \Nand I'm friends with Hayama-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.52,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew girls like that in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.36,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess that's how people see me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.69,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Girls who'd play guys like \Nsome kind of juggler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.69,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people say I'd \Nbe great in the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.70,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That's rather elaborate for a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.43,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you need at least 30 \Nsupporters in order to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:40.09,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That many? I'm impressed they got that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.71,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give the student who did \Nit a talking-to, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to do \Nit, just lose the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.21,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, isn't that the only way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:51.34,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but the thing is, Isshiki-san \Nis the only candidate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.72,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a vote of confidence, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:58.48,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It'd look really pathetic to \Nlose in a vote of confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:03.05,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have someone in mind \Nto give your campaign speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.34,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then this'll be quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:12.29,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it ends up a vote of confidence, \Nwe just need to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:15.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,she can definitely lose without \Ntaking any damage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In short, everyone just
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:21.34,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,needs to understand that it's \Nnot Isshiki's fault she lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.62,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If people lose confidence in her \Nbecause of her campaign speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.25,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,no one will give Isshiki a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.75,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's going to give that speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.39,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,we just need someone who can do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.65,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I can't approve of going about it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Your reason being?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.85,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.04,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It's too uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.47,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And a speech that breaks \Nconfidence in Isshiki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.54,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,would cause problems for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.37,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And even if it worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.30,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,do you think they'd have a second election?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.49,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.90,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much interest \Nin the student council,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.13,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,so if they just announce the results \Nwithout giving the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.35,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,no one will care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.53,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That means if they wanted to, they could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.56,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.56,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have said that. I take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.36,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,The only way is to back another candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.57,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,and have them win the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone willing to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.95,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't they already be \Nin the running by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.83,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.96,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try asking some \Npeople who might do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.96,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this one won't \Nbe solved right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.98,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:55.75,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.45,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Hiratsuka-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.09,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.98,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What are the standings right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.01,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.33,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Standings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.71,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A showdown to see who can \Ndo the most service,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and solve the most people's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The winner can order the \Nloser to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,We were doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.00,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.64,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did work together \Non several of those cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.25,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're all coming along well. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.68,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a relative assessment \Nof the three of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:37.74,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you one from my \Nown biased perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.23,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.05,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm just evaluating your results alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.70,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya's a step ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:49.05,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,But if I consider your \Nmethods and follow-ups,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.69,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita's faring better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.86,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,But either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:56.40,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd never get anywhere without \NYuigahama's contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.11,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying there is no winner yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.78,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:06.11,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Then even if our opinions are divided, \Nit won't be a problem, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.81,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:12.29,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I mean he and I don't have \Nto use the same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.99,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No point in working together \Nagainst our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.25,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the club going to do \Nuntil you reach a solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.72,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest free participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.34,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.79,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought that kind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.33,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of deception was what you \Nand I both hated most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.90,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.28,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.69,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.44,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.82,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nice kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.68,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've helped a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:51.00,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Despite appearances, there are \Ncertain people I'm partial to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that acceptable for a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.24,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in helping people \Ngrow through praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:00.50,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,But I give just as much discipline, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.17,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,With the way you do things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.72,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you meet someone \Nyou really want to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.78,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.17,phone_bar_13:14,Text,0000,0000,0000,,New Message
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.17,to_13:14,Text,0000,0000,0000,,To:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.17,Komachi_13:14,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:17.94,phone_bar_13:14,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:17.94,Totsuka_13:17,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuka Saika \N{\fs14}Hi, it's Saika
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.44,titlestop_13:19,TextTop,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner with My Cat                   Little Hero 5                The Theory of All Things                  Goatman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.44,titlesbot_13:19,TextBot,0000,0000,0000,,The Turing Test                         Childhood                              Still Bob                            Intergalactic
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.90,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.37,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a face I don't see often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.51,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need to run away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.50,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.46,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:50.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.26,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:55.80,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That super disgusted reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.52,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's everything I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.71,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's Yukino-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.28,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, same as ever, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.40,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.34,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And? Have there been any developments?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.41,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.66,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,She sent souvenirs home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She had them delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.64,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,She probably didn't want to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yet she bought souvenirs for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Dutiful of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.72,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:31.14,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,She hates us, but she doesn't \Nwant us to hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.53,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But there won't be any more \Nbig events at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:38.01,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess the rest will be \Npreparing for exams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.54,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:44.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's still the student council \Nelection and other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.57,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.53,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Meguri'll finally have to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.50,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Meguri, I bet
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.02,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,she asked Yukino-chan to be the \Nnext president, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.35,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,No? How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:03.10,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So Yukino-chan won't be student \Ncouncil president, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.73,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's just that I wasn't president.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.70,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.27,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hikigaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.97,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This totally takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.03,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Orimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.34,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought all my middle school classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:34.87,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,had been discarded into the \Ndeepest corner of my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.52,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And now Orimoto Kaori's name \Npops up, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.20,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikigaya, you go to Soubu High?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:48.13,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must be smart, then! I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.26,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You never talked to anyone, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.51,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.27,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought not! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.27,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I forcing myself to laugh? Creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:05.08,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be this is a friend \Nof yours, Hikigaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.33,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,When you say it like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:09.58,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,is it my imagination or does it sound \Nlike "You have a friend?" Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.28,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She was in my class in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.03,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Orimoto Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:19.13,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Yukinoshita Haruno, \NHikigaya-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:20.55,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.28,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.33,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, don't ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.29,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be weird to say I'm a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.21,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,An older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.18,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take the middle ground \Nand say I'm your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:37.01,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just say you're an \Nalumna from my high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.05,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.16,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you went to middle \Nschool with him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.69,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Got any interesting stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.62,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.94,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like love stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.16,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna hear about Hikigaya-kun's love life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.84,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Hikigaya asked me out once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.11,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.29,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:04.21,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,He had never even talked to me \Nbefore, so it was a total shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.38,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to you. I emailed you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:11.77,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,To the address you gave me out \Nof either sympathy or pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:14.59,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I made up the dumbest reasons to email you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.01,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,then bounced between excited and depressed, \Nwaiting to see if you'd respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:21.19,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Orimoto has no idea that happened, \Nand probably doesn't even remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.35,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Hikigaya-kun asked a girl out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.95,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was ages ago, so it \Ndoesn't really matter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:34.27,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! If you're at Soubu \NHigh, do you know Hayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.83,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.56,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that, Chika? He could \Nintroduce you to Hayama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.14,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's not a friend or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.95,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I can't see you having \Nany connection with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.21,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... This sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.21,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.55,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayato? Can you come out right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.80,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.22,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the donut place by the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.23,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Hayama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.46,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We'll email you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.44,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.24,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,He's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:17.86,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.96,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seemed like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.37,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.20,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,And why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.54,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd he have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.12,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:31.13,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That girl with the perm is the \Ngirl Hikigaya-kun used to like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:35.05,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Yukino-chan \Nwould react if she knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.04,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was great for killing some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.07,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.45,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for keeping me company, Hikigaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.40,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.86,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno-san really likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you nuts? She's just tormenting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:06.37,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't mess with people \Nshe's not interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.18,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.63,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,She either kills people she \Nlikes with too much attention
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:15.49,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,or thoroughly crushes \Npeople she doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.11,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:29.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.51,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to the club room today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.82,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.83,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we decided to talk with \NIroha-chan a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:51.59,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Like, we were hoping to \Nfigure out some plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:57.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,And... It didn't feel right \Nnot to let you know, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's just to listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:09.63,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been since I faced \Noff with Yukinoshita one-on-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.77,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the same now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:15.52,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita will reject my methods again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.15,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the same, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.20,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:32.36,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I think it'd be best \Nto find a candidate other than you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:35.36,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,and have you lose peacefully \Nin the final vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.09,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:41.09,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd feel better if I lost \Nto someone really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:45.98,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with a campaign pledge and \Nspeech for the candidate we select.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys come up with the pledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.77,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,that makes them a puppet candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:52.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:57.54,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If that candidate wins, \Nwhat happens to the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:01.12,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like we said, we just have \Nto find someone capable—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That'll just make it even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.72,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about what comes after, \Nyou'll realize there's not much point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a very good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:11.37,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Then what point is there \Nin doing it your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking strictly of this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,she'd avoid being elected and \Nlose the voters' confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,then decline to run in the by-election...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.16,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,"Speaking strictly of this case"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:24.88,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.64,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You avoided the problem last time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And? Was there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.27,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said there's no \Npoint in something that superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.21,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You're not changing that stance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.85,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.03,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:49.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:09.75,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly, \NYukinoshita Yukino Makes a Decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:24:09.13,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#04 And Then, Yuigahama Yui Makes a Declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:41.07,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.52,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:47.36,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,If we find someone good, it'll make \Nthings easier for me, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:49.63,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It'd have to be someone like Hayama, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:51.28,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Not Hayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:53.40,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it comes to it, I'll do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:55.28,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.74,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,No one else will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:00.67,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the only ones I can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:01.79,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:04.75,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.70,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help!
